===''Pokémon the Series''===
{{main|Giovanni (anime)}}
Giovanni appears in {{aniseries|PTS}} as the head of [[Team Rocket]]. Unlike the members of other prominent criminal organizations, he is a recurring character from {{aniseries|OS}} to {{aniseries|JN}}, usually keeping in contact with the [[Team Rocket trio]]. In {{aniseries|BW}}, he also appears in person to take on the role of direct antagonist at times.
